<section id="implementation">
    <h2>How to Start: Your Action Plan</h2>

    <h3>Week 1-2: Foundation</h3>
    <ol>
        <li>Stop snacking between meals</li>
        <li>No calories after dinner</li>
        <li>Black coffee only in morning</li>
        <li>Aim for 12-hour fasts</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Week 3-4: Progress</h3>
    <ol>
        <li>Push breakfast back 1 hour</li>
        <li>Achieve consistent 14-hour fasts</li>
        <li>Add electrolytes if needed</li>
        <li>Track how you feel, not just weight</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Month 2: Optimization</h3>
    <ol>
        <li>Reach 16:8 or 18:6</li>
        <li>Exercise before breaking fast</li>
        <li>Consider one 24-hour fast</li>
        <li>Monitor blood markers</li>
    </ol>

    <div class="key-point">
        <h3>The Lost Physiology</h3>
        <p>Modern humans have abandoned fasting – the very physiology that kept us healthy for millennia. We're designed to feast AND fast, not constantly graze. Reclaim this ancient healing mechanism.</p>
    </div>
